Package asgn1SoccerCompetition

A package that contains classes to model a soccer competition developed in cab302.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SportsCompetition
    A general purpose interface to model a sporting competition.
    SportsLeague
    A general purpose interface to model a sporting league.

    A general purpose interface to model a sporting team.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SoccerCompetition
    A class to model a soccer competition.
    SoccerLeague
    A class to model a soccer league.
    SoccerTeam
    A class to model a soccer team.
    SportsTeamForm
    A data structure to store the 'form' of a sports team, that is the the result (win, loss, draw) of the last 5 matches played.

Package asgn1SoccerCompetition Description

A package that contains classes to model a soccer competition developed in cab302. This could be extend to model a general sporting competition.
